Domestic violence is the leading cause of homelessness for women and children in America, and this week we can help.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FJcTTaX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My 6 year old, 16 year old, and 2 year old puppies The Pucketts

...

The Mary Parrish Center provides free housing for survivors to leave their abusers and stay off the street. In Mr Puckett's honor, I'm asking anyone who can afford it to donate $15 to Mary Parrish. 

https://www.maryparrish.org/donate

I also had them set up an Amazon Wishlist if you'd like to send items directly to survivors

https://www.amazon.com/hz/wishlist/ls/3USHUHIVSINQE?ref_=wl_share

